---
title: "Understand graph prior ramifications"
---

**Understand graph prior ramifications** is a pdf vignette. At present, pkgdown
(the R package used to create this website) does not support pdf vignettes; see
[pkgdown issue 781](https://github.com/r-lib/pkgdown/issues/781). Please access
**Understand graph prior ramifications** by installing Pv3Rs and calling
`vignette(topic = "understand-graph-prior", package = "Pv3Rs")` in R.
